Create an enterprise-grade Global Analytics Module for a Hotel Management SaaS (HMS) platform using:

- Laravel 13
- PHP 8.3+
- Modular Monolith Architecture
- Domain-Driven Design (DDD)
- Event-Driven Architecture
- Multi-Tenant SaaS
- REST API
- MySQL/PostgreSQL compatible design
- Redis caching
- Queue-based analytics processing

Architecture Context:
- Organization is the SaaS Tenant
- One Organization can have multiple Hotels
- Super Admin can access platform-wide analytics
- Hotel Admin can access organization-level analytics
- Hotel Manager can access assigned hotel analytics only

Business Roles:
1. Super Admin
2. Hotel Admin
3. Hotel Manager

IMPORTANT:
This module is ONLY for GLOBAL PLATFORM ANALYTICS used by Super Admin.

Purpose:
Provide enterprise-level SaaS analytics, business intelligence, operational monitoring, subscription metrics, revenue insights, booking analytics, tenant growth tracking, and platform health monitoring.

Generate COMPLETE enterprise architecture for Global Analytics Module.

